data.description: BRAND NEW MOVE-IN READY HOME W/ CLOSEOUT PRICING!! Introducing the Jasmine. Entertaining is a breeze w/ the kitchen, dining, and family room w/ cozy gas fireplace all in one large open space. One bedroom w/ full bath is also located on the 1st floor. The spacious owner's suite is conveniently located on 2nd floor and has a luxury owner's bath w/ 5 foot tiled shower w/ frameless shower door & double vanity. Two additional bedrooms share a full bath to finish out this unique plan. Design features include quartz countertops, pendant lights, & stainless gourmet appliances w/ gas cooktop & wall oven in the kitchen, oak tread stairs, LVP/tile flooring, upgraded painted cabinets, upgraded light fixtures/faucets, craftsman trim package.
